Out of all the shots fired at Koga he deflected everyone except the EMP which 
shoots him back disable on the ground.

Hades screams in pain as the mutiple nlast od spit hit him. He fires to shots 
at Spitfire while she is behind the rock.

Unitron retruns fire to the base defenses (with an "s" not a "c") get hit by 
a few shots.

Ares deflects one of the missiles but the other one knocked him over. He 
transforms and fires more shots at Rex.

Anubis gets hit by a missile but gets up and shoots the shit of the missile 
launcher.

Serpentor fires at smokescreen.
Serpentor: So we meet again.
While shooting at Rex he gets hit in the side of the face with spit cause him 
so go nearly unconscience.

Koga recieves the message from Set.
Koga: WHERE THE HELL HAVE YOU BEEN WE WERE WAITING FOR YOU AT THE ARK FOR 
BATTLE!!! GET RA OUT HERE AS SOON AS YOU CAN!!! AAAAHHHHH!!!
Koga screams as the claws go in his back.
